snippet.title: Touhou Danmaku Kagura Phantasia Lost  Trailer 03
snippet.description:
The Steam version will be released on February 8th, 2024!!!
https://store.steampowered.com/app/2190220/_/

A Standard Edition and a Deluxe Edition are being scheduled for release.
The Standard Edition has a total of 68 music scores included. In addition, a total of 102 music scores will be released over 4 DLCs!

What's more, a collaboration song between Toby Fox & ZUN 『U.N. Owen Was Hero?』 will be released, as a free DLC, at the same time as the release of the Steam Edition!
